Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.35,0:16:18.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裏既是狂都…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.04,0:16:19.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是經都
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.00,0:16:20.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是境都吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.99,0:16:21.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,京都
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.46,0:16:22.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,興都
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.12,0:16:22.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凶都
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.74,0:16:23.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狂都
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.16,0:16:23.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,境都
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.53,0:16:24.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,經都
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.05,0:16:24.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,京都
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.63,0:16:25.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,興都凶都狂都境都京都…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.98,0:16:27.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夠啦——!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.69,0:16:30.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全不知道你們在搞甚麼!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.30,0:16:33.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使是個玩笑 也不是完全沒有意義的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.70,0:16:39.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有任何意義的孩子有甚麼用呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.62,0:16:46.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們想期待你那像孩童一般的可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.14,0:16:48.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是非常亂來的遊戲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.94,0:16:50.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓毗舍丸做她的對手不正是她的心願嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.32,0:16:52.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見啦 琴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.50,0:16:55.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.58,0:16:57.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還沒同意呢!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.85,0:16:59.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不承認這是議會的决定!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.41,0:17:03.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要服從「最初之人」和規定 !
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.18,0:17:03.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鞍馬!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.88,0:17:09.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這可是正式的考試哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.15,0:17:12.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你其實是很清楚的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.68,0:17:15.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為你也是很想見見媽媽的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.79,0:17:16.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,俄狄浦斯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.60,0:17:18.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.57,0:17:21.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是要等得花兒都謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.52,0:17:26.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來這自主行動 才是重逢的關鍵呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.54,0:17:26.75,writings4,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(193,227)\frz3.394}是姐姐!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.17,0:17:26.75,note,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}稱號 狼吞虎嚥全收集\N隨身物品 精神 香口膠 糖\N零用錢 兩個人3日元
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.96,0:17:26.75,writings4,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(199,255)\frz4.096}出不去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.97,0:17:30.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你應該會理解我們吧 琴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.14,0:17:34.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那幫傻瓜都鬧瘋了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.28,0:17:37.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦啊 稻荷?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.35,0:17:43.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…認為人類的外表也很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.07,0:17:45.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我也不是你们的母親
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.10,0:17:50.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我也明白你們想見家人的心情啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.88,0:17:53.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 只此一次 我就奉陪到底吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.77,0:17:54.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行! 别…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.72,0:17:58.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,固執的臭男人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.19,0:18:06.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.93,0:18:08.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可別妨著我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.22,0:18:10.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖怪!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.58,0:18:12.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你丫才是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.98,0:18:14.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底在搞甚麼啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.97,0:18:15.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人類!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.03,0:18:21.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是一直倍受各位照顧啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.97,0:18:26.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 我覺得對小孩子這麼做可不好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.13,0:18:28.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別把單方面的期待強加於人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.75,0:18:31.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我總是被大人背叛嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.70,0:18:36.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來彼此都不太走運呢!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.88,0:18:43.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我站住!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.97,0:18:45.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼認真幹甚麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.61,0:18:46.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白痴!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.76,0:18:49.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我現在就讓你丫閉嘴! 你這鬼!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.06,0:18:54.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是華麗的兄妹對打…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.06,0:18:59.34,writings5,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fay-0.2\frz359.191\pos(193,247)}為甚麼搞不壞!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.05,0:18:59.97,writings5,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fay-0.2\frz356.178\pos(180,278)}他作弊。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.39,0:18:59.97,writings5,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fay-0.2\frz359.191\pos(218,248)}用作弊器改角色太卑鄙啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.60,0:19:02.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這下場挺不錯的嘛 公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.69,0:19:08.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這臭人類!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.66,0:19:11.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡 真是氣死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.73,0:19:13.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過這招如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.52,0:19:14.57,writings5,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fay-0.2\frz359.191\pos(180,247)}上啊 琴!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.02,0:19:14.57,writings5,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fay-0.2\frz359.191\pos(176,277)}做掉它!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.65,0:19:20.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說啊 明惠
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.55,0:19:23.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有個事情一直想問你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.67,0:19:27.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一張嘴就是抱怨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.40,0:19:31.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是卻把那些孩子當成寶一樣對待
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.66,0:19:34.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們之間是沒有秘密的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.56,0:19:35.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧 明惠
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.11,0:19:40.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你最捨不得的 到底是哪一方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.86,0:19:48.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看見了嗎 這精密機器!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.52,0:19:51.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必殺——
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.80,0:19:54.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,家電破消滅擊!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.69,0:19:55.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白——痴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.71,0:19:56.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白痴!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.17,0:20:02.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等…等一下!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.45,0:20:03.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暫停! 暫停!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.07,0:20:42.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然還是很可惜啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.56,0:20:52.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣真的好嗎
