Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.37,0:20:54.62,writings6,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fay-0.2\frz359.191\pos(233,244)}出去出去 出去出去出去出去出去!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.61,0:20:54.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是對他們保密吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.96,0:21:07.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翔子 你是不是有點失落?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.13,0:21:08.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好疼!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.75,0:21:10.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,疼疼疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.25,0:21:12.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 我都說好疼了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.10,0:21:21.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是頭疼呀~
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.93,0:21:24.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管長多大 都還總是打打鬧鬧的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.15,0:21:27.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直這麼縱容他們 是你的不對哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.92,0:21:29.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.84,0:21:31.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又能見面了 我好高興!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.88,0:21:36.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我也一直都在等待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.73,0:21:46.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,病毒?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.19,0:21:55.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一旦話說出口 我就會付諸行動
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.01,0:22:03.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的言語 就是我的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.40,0:22:12.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快看! 是媽媽啦媽媽!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.54,0:22:13.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.11,0:22:19.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來 快告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.70,0:22:21.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吾王 吾主
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.28,0:22:24.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您之願即是我之望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.27,0:22:28.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…想…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.93,0:22:35.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想回家啦——
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.47,0:23:54.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古都!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.44,0:23:58.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你變漂亮了呢 小公主
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.53,0:24:03.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你老了很多呢 鞍馬
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.07,0:24:06.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您還是那麼美麗 古都
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.11,0:24:08.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.71,0:24:14.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被女人親了…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.91,0:24:16.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被个女人親了啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.68,0:24:19.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.11,0:24:22.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都長這麼大了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.49,0:24:26.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在能自己一個人睡覺啦 明惠?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.08,0:24:28.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好煩…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.80,0:24:30.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你都有了這麼多小孩啦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.98,0:24:31.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.66,0:24:33.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琴
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.29,0:24:40.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起啊 我好像誤會了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.05,0:24:42.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能和我重歸於好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.86,0:24:46.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.13,0:24:54.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能回來真是太好了 古都大人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.50,0:24:56.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您一直 在等待著我們的迎接吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.48,0:25:00.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.42,0:25:01.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然不是很明白
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.80,0:25:02.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.68,0:25:09.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.48,0:25:15.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們也好想回家 所以拜托啦
